🔧 Components Required for Smart Stick Project

Here’s everything you need to build this setup:

Arduino Uno – the main controller
Ultrasonic Sensor (HC-SR04) – to detect obstacles
Buzzer – gives sound alert
LED – visual alert indicator
Resistor (220Ω) – for LED safety
Jumper Wires – to connect components
Breadboard (optional) – for easy connections
Power Source (USB or battery) – to run Arduino
